## ggplot2 structure  

1. Data  

2. Layers `geom_*()` and `stat_*()`  

3. Aesthetics `aes()`  

4. Scales `scale_*()`  

5. Coordinate system `coord_*()`  

6. Facets `facet_*()` arrangement of the data into a grid of plots **!!!**  

```{r facet}
usda %>% 
  filter(Year %in% c(2010:2013)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(Value))+
  geom_histogram()+
  facet_grid(Year~State)
```

